What this agent actually is

A system that connects to your financial accounts, understands your goals, and gives real-time, personalized money guidance—automated, data-aware, and conversational.

Breakdown of how to build it
1. Input Layer

Connect accounts (Robinhood, Zerodha, banks, crypto wallets).

Pull transactions, holdings, SIPs, dividends, income, spending.

Normalize everything into one schema.

2. Brain / Reasoning Layer

Real-time Q&A (“Why is my portfolio down this week?”).

Predictive insights (risk, diversification, SIP performance).

Financial models (asset allocation, tax impact, rebalancing).

Goals engine (retirement, house, emergency fund).

3. Output Layer

     

Automated recommendations (adjust SIP, rebalance, save X more).

Alerts (“Your credit card bill due in 2 days”).

Monthly financial report.

Perspectives / Use-Case Angles
A. As a Wealth Analyst

Tracks your portfolio.

Explains your gains/losses in simple language.

Shows allocations, risk, factor exposure.

